DiffAnalyzer
This class implements a general diff analyzer.

This class is used to provide the numbers of changed lines in different file types of a specific commit.
FileDiff
This abstract class represents a general file diff.
FileDiff.FileType
Enumeration for defining the type of file diff for a specific object.
